import { 
    PageContainer, 
    ContentContainer,
    LeftContentContainer,
    RightContentContainer,
    Divider,
} from './home-page.styles';
import Profile from '../profile/profile.component';

const HomePage = () => (
    <PageContainer>
        <Profile
         imageSrc='../../assets/ProfilePic.jpg' 
         profileName='Ricardo Villada'
         profession='Software Developer'
         summary='Software Development student wanting to make a cereer using AWS and Python'
         ></Profile>
         <ContentContainer>
            <LeftContentContainer>

            </LeftContentContainer>
            <Divider></Divider>
            <RightContentContainer>
                <label>Projects</label>
            </RightContentContainer>
         </ContentContainer>
    </PageContainer>
)

export default HomePage;
